commit.message:
Makefile.am (BOOT_CLASS_PATH_DIR): Only contain libgcj.jar.

2006-07-07  Gary Benson  <gbenson@redhat.com>

	* Makefile.am (BOOT_CLASS_PATH_DIR): Only contain libgcj.jar.
	* Makefile.in: Regenerate.
